1
00:00:47,160 --> 00:00:47,890
Come with me.

2
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:49,880
Ou Shaowen.

3
00:00:52,800 --> 00:00:53,760
She is Feifei.

4
00:00:54,760 --> 00:00:55,490
Not Dailing.

5
00:00:59,480 --> 00:01:00,740
I don't care who she is.

6
00:01:01,160 --> 00:01:02,690
She must come with me today.

7
00:01:03,440 --> 00:01:05,840
Let's see if you have what it takes.

8
00:01:11,240 --> 00:01:11,880
Ang Wei.

9
00:01:13,560 --> 00:01:14,760
It's been five years.

10
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:17,280
Do you want her to die with you again?

11
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:20,480
Do you have the right to interfere with what I, Ang Wei, do?

12
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:28,100
You have the wrong person.

13
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:29,000
I am Feifei.

14
00:01:30,440 --> 00:01:31,440
Not some Dailing.

15
00:01:40,039 --> 00:01:40,880
Ou Shaowen.

16
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:43,600
Don't think just because you have Siam's backing,

17
00:01:43,600 --> 00:01:44,860
I won't dare touch you.

18
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:48,120
Get out of my territory.

19
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:06,520
Dailing.

20
00:02:07,720 --> 00:02:09,449
No matter what your purpose is,

21
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:12,490
I will absolutely not let go again.

22
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:43,720
Dear family and friends,

23
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:47,620
thank you for coming to see my husband off on his final journey.

24
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,560
It's the rainy season in Mancheng,

25
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:51,760
yet not a single drop of rain has fallen.

26
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:53,440
It must be that my husband

27
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:55,240
cannot rest in peace.

28
00:02:58,320 --> 00:02:59,050
Mrs. Biyang,

29
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:00,650
my condolences.

30
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:04,520
Madam,

31
00:03:04,920 --> 00:03:06,840
can you give us the authorization documents

32
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:07,840
for the Leo route?

33
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:12,480
My husband's body isn't even cold yet,

34
00:03:12,760 --> 00:03:16,120
and you're already rushing here to demand the shipping lanes.

35
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:17,280
How he died,

36
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:19,680
don't you know in your hearts?

37
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:23,620
I haven't gone to Tangong to demand an explanation yet,

38
00:03:24,079 --> 00:03:26,480
and you're already here demanding things.

39
00:03:28,079 --> 00:03:30,120
If I don't give it to you today,

40
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:32,450
are you going to snatch it by force?

41
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:33,560
Madam.

42
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:48,810
My condolences, Madam.

43
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:52,290
You said Mr. Biyang died with a grievance.

44
00:03:52,320 --> 00:03:53,579
Then I have a proposal.

45
00:03:53,880 --> 00:03:56,480
If I can make the dead speak,

46
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:58,880
will you hand over the route

47
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,850
to Mr. Angwei for safekeeping?

48
00:04:01,760 --> 00:04:02,840
Make him speak?

49
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:05,760
I'd like to see

50
00:04:06,200 --> 00:04:07,660
what a little girl like you

51
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:08,920
can do

52
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:10,800
to make the dead appear.

53
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:17,160
It hasn't rained in Mancheng for over ten days.

54
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,680
If I can bring rain today,

55
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:22,680
it means Mr. Biyang has acknowledged Mr. Angwei.

56
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:02,240
Miss Feifei,

57
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:04,340
do you need my help?

58
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:05,640
Angwei.

59
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:07,250
Mrs. Biyang.

60
00:05:07,960 --> 00:05:09,090
I didn't invite you,

61
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,450
but you came on your own.

62
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:13,770
My husband died in your Tan Palace.

63
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:15,530
It's his funeral today.

64
00:05:15,960 --> 00:05:17,560
Don't cause any more trouble

65
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:18,740
or make a scene.

66
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:20,080
Mrs. Biyang,

67
00:05:20,760 --> 00:05:21,760
don't be so hasty.

68
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:24,080
Why not listen to Mr. Biyang's opinion?

69
00:05:27,520 --> 00:05:29,120
What do you say, Miss Feifei?

70
00:05:30,400 --> 00:05:31,720
The timing is perfect.

71
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:34,800
The rain enhancement device is starting up.

72
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,800
Mr. Biyang is about to show himself.

73
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:03,480
I knew it was you coming back.

74
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:06,160
Dailing.

75
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:21,880
From now on,

76
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:25,080
you and your life

77
00:06:26,320 --> 00:06:27,080
are mine.

78
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:30,520
What about what you promised me?

79
00:06:31,840 --> 00:06:33,159
We agreed

80
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:35,680
that I'd help you get the route

81
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:37,810
and you'd grant me one request.

82
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:40,180
You can't go back on your word.

83
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,530
What do you want me to grant you?

84
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:46,360
Now that you have the route,

85
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:49,800
who will you assign to contact the ship owners,

86
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:50,760
check the data,

87
00:06:51,400 --> 00:06:53,280
and handle the customs clearance?

88
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,540
Who will you give it to?

89
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,450
So you were aiming for the route

90
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,880
from the very beginning.

91
00:07:02,520 --> 00:07:03,780
That's not important.

92
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:06,650
To keep an eye on this route,

93
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:10,160
I am a hundred times more suitable

94
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,840
than your thugs.

95
00:07:13,520 --> 00:07:15,780
After all, we rely on brains to do things,

96
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:17,320
not fists.

97
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,440
Choosing me

98
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:21,560
is highly beneficial to you.

99
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:23,500
I've asked around.

100
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:25,560
About your past with the Dai family,

101
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:28,560
those subordinates won't listen to you at all.

102
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:30,450
I'm warning you.

103
00:07:32,400 --> 00:07:34,659
Don't mess with those old subordinates.

104
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,800
So you've kept them

105
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:47,560
to protect them.

106
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,400
Don't worry.

107
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:01,720
I will never touch the Dai family's subordinates.

108
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:07,440
Fine.

109
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,320
Since you put it that way,

110
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:12,760
it does no harm to me.

111
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:15,320
Follow me.

112
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,440
From now on,

113
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:22,720
you can live here.

114
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,840
I won't restrict your personal freedom,

115
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:26,840
but you can't bring outsiders here.

116
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:29,280
I'll bring a contract over later,

117
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:30,760
for a period of three months.

118
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:32,820
Sign it when you've made up your mind.

119
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,280
Young master.

120
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:51,800
The contract is drafted.

121
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,280
From now on,

122
00:09:17,040 --> 00:09:18,770
you are my personal secretary.

123
00:09:19,520 --> 00:09:21,960
I won't allow you to get close to any man.

124
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:25,500
Can you do that?

125
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:27,400
Of course.

126
00:09:28,800 --> 00:09:29,400
Follow me.

127
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:31,720
The traitor who leaked the information to Ou Shaowen

128
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:32,650
has been caught.

129
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:37,400
Mr. Aung Wei, I swear to God.

130
00:09:37,680 --> 00:09:39,400
I didn't leak anything about the route.

131
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:40,520
I just met with the people

132
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:41,280
from Siam Group.

133
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:42,760
Even if you gave me a hundred times the courage,

134
00:09:42,760 --> 00:09:43,800
I wouldn't dare betray you

135
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:44,760
or the Sihai Group.

136
00:09:44,760 --> 00:09:46,820
The score I'm settling with you today

137
00:09:48,160 --> 00:09:49,690
isn't just about the route.

138
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:57,850
It's also about that incident from years ago.

139
00:09:59,200 --> 00:09:59,560
What?

140
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:02,400
Come in.

141
00:10:10,880 --> 00:10:11,880
Look at this face.

142
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:14,060
Does it look familiar?

143
00:10:14,240 --> 00:10:15,040
Aren't you...

144
00:10:15,560 --> 00:10:16,760
Why are you here?

145
00:10:17,800 --> 00:10:19,600
And you still say you don't know.

146
00:10:21,560 --> 00:10:22,120
Tell me,

147
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:24,080
what really happened back then?
